Package: datadict
Type: Package
Title: Generate a Data Dictionary
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Ama", family = "Nyame-Mensah", 
    email = "ama@anyamemensah.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A focused toolset for creating and managing data dictionaries. 
    Allows users to document datasets by extracting variable labels and 
    distributions, restructure complex metadata by expanding delimited 
    entries into tidy formats, and verify the integrity of dictionary 
    mappings.
